---
import Strava from '../components/Strava.astro';
import Navigation from './Navigation.astro';
---
<main>
    <Navigation />
    <section class="header-container">
        <ul class="social-links">
            <li><h1 class="title">Jacky Choi</h1></li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/smallnumbers0" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-github"></i></a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jackykchoi/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a></li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Penn Engineering 2027</h2>
    </section>
    <section class="summary-container">
        <p>Welcome! I am currently learning the art of Computer Science at the University of Pennsylvania. This site showcases my journey with Computer Science. I spend most of my time in balancing my academic interests like machine learning, health sciences, and data visualization, along with my athletic pursuits as a distance runner. These experiences sparked my interest into exploring data and programming leading me to work on projects using Python, Javascript, and various Web Development tools.
    </section>

    <section class="skills-container">
        <div class="skill-card"></div>
        <div class="skill-card"></div>
        <div class="skill-card"></div>
        <div class="skill-card"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- <Strava /> -->

</main>

<style>
    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 10px;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        --orange-color: rgb(226, 99, 20);
    }
    main {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        width: 50%;
        min-width: 400px;
    }
    h1, h2 {
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: aliceblue;
    }

    p {
        line-height: 1.5rem;
    }

    .header-container {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.3rem;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .title {
        font-size: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
        color: var(--orange-color);
    }

    .summary-container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .summary-container, p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: aliceblue;
        padding: 1rem 0;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .social-links {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .social-links li {
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .social-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: aliceblue;
        transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .social-links a:hover {
        color: var(--orange-color);
    }

    i {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .skills-container {
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        justify-content: left;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;

    }

    .skill-card {
        border: 1px solid rgb(255, 255, 255);
        width: 100%;
        height: 250px;
        min-width: 280px;
        max-width: 370px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15) 0px 2px 4px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 0px 2px 4px;
    }

    .skill-card:hover {
        border: 1px solid var(--orange-color);
        box-shadow: rgb(226, 99, 20) 0px 2px 4px, rgb(226, 99, 20) 0px 2px 4px;
        transition: 0.7s;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
        main {
            min-width: 800px;
        }
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 900px) {
        .skills-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        main {
            min-width: 370px;
        }
    }

</style>